summary:
I use the power of Data Science, AI and Machine Learning to drive breakthroughs in biotechnological and biomedical research and turn ideas into practical, life-changing solutions. I thrive when I work on innovative projects and do things that have never been done before. Continuously learning and exploring emerging technologies and new, more efficient approaches helps me to maintain state-of-the art expertise in a fast-changing field of computational biology. I believe that teamwork is the key to success and that sharing knowledge and working in close cooperation within and across team boundaries can unleash true innovative potential and create a real value for the team, organisation and the public.

Feel free to contact me because I am always open for collaboration and new challenges.

And check my personal website if you would like to know more about my work, science and programming.

--> www.betterlearntocode.com
